      <title>Linux下的cut、paste及expend</title>
      <link href="/2021/11/03/Linux%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84cut%E3%80%81paste%E5%8F%8Aexpend/"/>
      <url>/2021/11/03/Linux%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84cut%E3%80%81paste%E5%8F%8Aexpend/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="linux下的cutpaste及expend">Linux下的cut、paste及expend</h1><h2 id="cut命令的使用">cut命令的使用</h2><p><strong>cut基本格式</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cut [OPTIONS] [FILES]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>常用参数选项</strong></p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">参数</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">-c</td><td>以字符为单位进行分割</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;">-d</td><td>自定义分割符，默认是制表符</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">-f</td><td>以区域为单位进行分割，常与 -d 选项一起使用</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;">-n</td><td>取消分割多字节字符，仅与 -b 选项同用</td></tr></tbody></table><p>从对 cut 命令的选项描述来看，该命令一般通过三种单位进行分割：字节、字符、域 。</p><h2 id="paste命令的使用">paste命令的使用</h2><p><strong>paste基本格式</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">paste [OPTIONS] [FILES]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>常用参数选项</strong></p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">参数</th><th style="text-align: left;">描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">-s</td><td style="text-align: left;">将每个文件合并成行，而不是按行粘贴（即每个文件中的内容占一行，而不是每个文件取行合并成新行）</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;">-d</td><td style="text-align: left;">自定义分隔符，默认为制表符（Tab）</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">-z</td><td style="text-align: left;">按行粘贴，类似于 cat 多个文件</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="expend命令的使用">expend命令的使用</h2><p><strong>expend基本格式</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">expand [OPTIONS] [FILES]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>常用参数选项</strong></p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">参数</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">-i, --initial</td><td>不转换非空白符后的制表符</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;">-t, --tabs=NUMBER</td><td>指定一个tab替换为多少个空格，而不是默认的 8</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">-t, --tabs=LIST</td><td>指定制表符位置列表，用逗号分隔</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;">--help</td><td>显示帮助信息</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">--version</td><td>输出版本信息</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="linux中将命令行运行结果放到文件中">Linux中将命令行运行结果放到文件中</h2><p><strong>仅转向不显示</strong></p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">命令</th><th>解释</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">ls &gt; test.txt</td><td>把输出转向到指定的文件，如文件已存在的话也会重新写入，文件原内容不会保留</td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;">ls &gt;&gt; test.txt</td><td>是把输出附向到文件的后面，文件原内容会保留下来</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="problem-1">Problem 1</h2><p><strong>Question</strong></p><p>Try to run "cat /etc/passwd" in your shell, and read the result, each line of which is composed of some words separated by ':'. Then please read the manuals of UNIX utilities "cut" and "paste" (e.g., man cut; info paste), and understand how to use them. Our target is to cut the 1st word (i.e., field 1 - the user names) and the 6th word (i.e., field 6 - HOME directories) in each line from file /etc/passwd, and store them in 2 separated new files. Then we paste the 2 files together into a new file with only 2 word columns, and these 2 columns are separated by one tab character in each line. The expected result looks like, <strong>Answer</strong></p><p>运行<code>cat /etc/passwd</code>可以看到，文件是按域进行分隔的，间隔符为<code>:</code></p><p>现在我们提取每一行的第一个域（这里以前5行为例），命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat /etc/passwd | head -n 5 | cut -d : -f 1 &gt; p1_1.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p1_1.txt</span></span><br><span class="line">root</span><br><span class="line">daemon</span><br><span class="line">bin</span><br><span class="line">sys</span><br><span class="line">sync</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同理取出第六个域（这里以前12行为例），命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat /etc/passwd | head -n 5 | cut -d : -f 6 &gt; p1_2.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p1_2.txt</span></span><br><span class="line">/root</span><br><span class="line">/usr/sbin</span><br><span class="line">/bin</span><br><span class="line">/dev</span><br><span class="line">/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过paste命令来组合两个文本合成为p1.txt，命令如下:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> paste p1_1.txt p1_2.txt &gt; p1.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p1.txt</span></span><br><span class="line">root/root</span><br><span class="line">daemon/usr/sbin</span><br><span class="line">bin/bin</span><br><span class="line">sys/dev</span><br><span class="line">sync/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>注：在终端显示是以Tab键为间隔，在Markdown里不知道为什么会这样</p></blockquote><h2 id="problem-2">Problem 2</h2><p><strong>Question</strong></p><p>Please read the manual of UNIX utility "expand", and change the tab character in the result of Problem 2 into many space characters, while the word alignment keeps and the 2nd word always begins on the 20th column. The expected result looks like,</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root               /root</span><br><span class="line">daemon             /usr/sbin</span><br><span class="line">bin                /bin</span><br><span class="line">sys                /dev</span><br><span class="line">sync               /bin</span><br><span class="line">games              /usr/games</span><br><span class="line">man                /var/cache/man</span><br><span class="line">lp                 /var/spool/lpd</span><br><span class="line">mail               /var/mail</span><br><span class="line">news               /var/spool/news</span><br><span class="line">landscape          /var/lib/landscape</span><br><span class="line">postgres           /var/lib/postgresql</span><br><span class="line">uucp               /var/spool/uucp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Answer</strong></p><p>使用expend命令来实现所需功能，命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p1.txt &gt; p2.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p2.txt</span></span><br><span class="line">root/root</span><br><span class="line">daemon/usr/sbin</span><br><span class="line">bin/bin</span><br><span class="line">sys/dev</span><br><span class="line">sync/bin</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> expand -t 19 p2.txt &gt; p2_final.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p2_final.txt</span></span><br><span class="line">root               /root</span><br><span class="line">daemon             /usr/sbin</span><br><span class="line">bin                /bin</span><br><span class="line">sys                /dev</span><br><span class="line">sync               /bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="problem-3">Problem 3</h2><p><strong>Question</strong></p><p>Everything similar as in Problem 2, but try to show the results in a manner like below.</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root:</span><br><span class="line">/root</span><br><span class="line">daemon:</span><br><span class="line">/usr/sbin</span><br><span class="line">bin:</span><br><span class="line">/bin</span><br><span class="line">sys:</span><br><span class="line">/dev</span><br><span class="line">sync:</span><br><span class="line">/bin</span><br><span class="line">games:</span><br><span class="line">/usr/games</span><br><span class="line">man:</span><br><span class="line">/var/cache/man</span><br><span class="line">lp:</span><br><span class="line">/var/spool/lpd</span><br><span class="line">mail:</span><br><span class="line">/var/mail</span><br><span class="line">news:</span><br><span class="line">/var/spool/news</span><br><span class="line">landscape:</span><br><span class="line">/var/lib/landscape</span><br><span class="line">postgres:</span><br><span class="line">/var/lib/postgresql</span><br><span class="line">uucp:</span><br><span class="line">/var/spool/uucp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Answer</strong></p><p>为了实现所需的效果，命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> paste -d <span class="string">&#x27;:&#x27;</span> p1_1.txt p1_2.txt &gt; p3_1.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p3_1.txt</span></span><br><span class="line">root:/root</span><br><span class="line">daemon:/usr/sbin</span><br><span class="line">bin:/bin</span><br><span class="line">sys:/dev</span><br><span class="line">sync:/bin</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cut p3_1.txt -d / -f 1 &gt; p3_2.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p3_2.txt</span></span><br><span class="line">root:</span><br><span class="line">daemon:</span><br><span class="line">bin:</span><br><span class="line">sys:</span><br><span class="line">sync:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> paste -d <span class="string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span> p3_2.txt p1_2.txt &gt; p3.txt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> cat p3.txt</span></span><br><span class="line">root:</span><br><span class="line">/root</span><br><span class="line">daemon:</span><br><span class="line">/usr/sbin</span><br><span class="line">bin:</span><br><span class="line">/bin</span><br><span class="line">sys:</span><br><span class="line">/dev</span><br><span class="line">sync:</span><br><span class="line">/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="problem-4">Problem 4</h2><p><strong>Find what Ubuntu is from www.wikipedia.org; briefly explain why this name is chosen.</strong></p><p>Ubuntu is named after the Nguni philosophy of ubuntu, which Canonical indicates means "humanity to others" with a connotation of "I am what I am because of who we all are".</p><h2 id="probelm-5">Probelm 5</h2><p><strong>Watch the video Revolution OS, and briefly answer,</strong></p><p><strong>1. What application greatly motivated companies to use Linux instead of Windows?</strong></p><p><strong>Answer:</strong> Apache.</p><p><strong>2. (Optional) What Richard Stallman means in his Han Solo analogy when FSF is given the Linus Torvalds Award?</strong></p><p><strong>Answer:</strong> Because the operating system is the combination of the GNU and Linux.</p>]]></content>
      
      
